@* Hero：Bootstrap 約束閱讀寬／間距；外觀仍為 helix *@

<div class="hero">

  <div class="container px-3 px-lg-4 px-xl-5 pt-2">

    <div class="row justify-content-center gx-0 gx-lg-4 gx-xl-5 text-center">

      <div class="col-12 col-lg-11 col-xl-10 col-xxl-9">

        <div class="hero-tag reveal">

          <div class="hero-tag-dot"></div>

          Windows  ·  WPF  ·  .NET 8  ·  x64

        </div>

        <h1 class="reveal">把分散的工具<br><em>整合進一個 Shell</em></h1>

        <p class="hero-sub reveal mx-auto px-1 px-sm-0">

          Helix Studio 是以 Windows 桌面為核心的模組化工具主機。

          不同場域，不同工具，統一管理、部署與診斷。

        </p>

        <div class="hero-cta reveal d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center align-items-center gap-2 gap-sm-3">

          <a href="#contact" class="btn-lg btn-lg-accent">

            預約 Demo

            <svg width="13" height="13" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12h15m0 0l-6-6m6 6l-6 6"/></svg>

          </a>

          <a href="#import" class="btn-lg btn-lg-ghost">了解運作方式</a>

        </div>

        <p class="hero-meta reveal px-2">製造業 · 設備商 · 有內部工具需求的中型企業</p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>



  <div class="container-xl px-3 px-lg-4 px-xl-5 mt-4 mt-lg-5">

    <div class="row justify-content-center gx-0">

      <div class="col-12 min-w-0">

        <div class="hero-shell-wrap reveal position-relative">

          <div class="hero-shell-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>

          @await Html.PartialAsync("Partials/_LandingStaticShellFrame")

        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</div>


